Company Overview of Schooner Investment Group LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Schooner Investment Group LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to investment companies, institutions, financial intermediaries, and pooled investment vehicles. It manages separate client focused portfolios. The firm also manages equity and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. Schooner Investment Group LLC was founded in January 2008 and is based in Wayne, Pennsylvania.


