Firm Overview - Schooner Investment Group LLC

















































 


Site Name Call Us Today (484) 580-8086
info@schoonerfunds.com




Firm Overview
Schooner Investment Group, LLC is an SEC Registered Investment Advisor headquartered in Wayne, Pennsylvania. We offer investment management services, with a focus on sustainable and risk-reducing investment strategies, to institutions and individuals seeking to preserve and build capital. Founded in 2008, the firm specializes in alternative funds, separate accounts, and private investment funds. Assets raised in the alternative fund space total $750+ million since 2009.
Access Schooner's Form ADV by clicking here.


 (484) 580-8086
Click here for Schooner Form ADV


 676 E. Swedesford Road
Suite 130Wayne,  PA 19087

